headline: RBC Capital Lowers Mosaic (MOS) Outlook Following Earnings Miss and Cash Flow Concerns
summary: The Mosaic Company (NYSE:MOS) is included among the 13 Best Long-Term Dividend Stocks to Invest in Right Now. On February 26, RBC Capital lowered its price recommendation on The Mosaic Company (NYSE:MOS) to $28 from $29.
